## Project Overview
This repository consists of two customer interviews. Customers shared their thoughts on automatic insights generated by the AI feature. See 'interview-guide.txt' in `context/` folder for an interview guide. 

## Core Principles
- **Plan first** -- enter plan mode before non-trivial tasks; save plans to `plans`
- **Verify after** -- compile/render and confirm output at the end of every task
- **[LEARN] tags** -- when corrected, save `[LEARN:category] wrong → right` to `MEMORY.md`

